<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">Hi,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">The mxm which is part of MOFED 1.5.3 supports OMPI 1.6.0.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">The mxm upgrade is needed to work with OMPI 1.6.3&#43;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">Please remove mxm from your cluster nodes (rpm -e mxm)<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">Install latest from&nbsp; <a href="http://mellanox/com/products/mxm/">
http://mellanox/com/products/mxm/</a><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">Compile ompi 1.6.3, add following to its configure line: ./configure --with-openib=/usr --with-mxm=/opt/mellanox/mxm &lt;...&gt;)<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal">Regards<o:p></o:p></p>
